    "Explanation": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "<b>Power (\\(P\\))</b> is calculated as:<br><br>\\(P = I \\times V = 2.0\\,A \\times 230\\,V = 460\\,W\\)<br><br>Direct multiplication gives option (d)."
    },
